# 懵然不知
(pos:形容詞 / 成語)
<explanation>
yue:完全唔知、一啲都唔知嘅樣貌（量詞：無）
eng:completely ignorant; have no idea at all
<eg>
yue:佢對呢件事懵然不知，仲以為係好事嚟㗎。 (keoi5 deoi3 ni1 gin6 si6 mong5 jin4 bat1 zi1, zung6 ji5 wei6 hai6 hou2 si6 lei4 gaa3.)
eng:He had no idea about this matter at all, and still thought it was a good thing. [end of text]


